  "description": "Add Bountiful compatibility to other mods",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/1139352.svg\" alt=\"title\" width=\"169\" height=\"25\" /></p>\n<div><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-blue?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.minecraftforge.net%2Fnet%2Fminecraftforge%2Fforge%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-lime?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fneoforged.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Fabric-yellow?style=plastic&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ffabricmc.net%2F\" alt=\"Static Badge\" /></div>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod add more bounties to <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bountiful\">Bountiful</a> to make it compatible with other mods</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/ExtraBounties/screen.png?raw=true\" alt=\"image\" width=\"574\" height=\"260\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Check the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/DataThings/blob/Extra-Bounties/README.md\">readme</a> and create a pull-request if you want help this mod!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Mod compat suggestions <a href=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/DataThings/issues\">here</a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extra-bounties/relations/dependencies\">Full list of mods included </a></span></p>",
